      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For that high-end aesthetic, you should aim for a look that embodies classic, understated power, which often translates to a very polished, traditional appearance. Think well-groomed, impeccably dressed individuals who project quiet confidence rather than flashy ostentation. The visual profile should lean towards timeless elegance—think classic tailoring, muted but expensive colors, and a very curated sense of personal presentation. This look is about inherited taste and established social standing, not fleeting trends.",
